        </nav>

        <div class="card">
            <h2 class="card-title">RPay API Documentation</h2>
            <p>Integrasikan payment gateway QRIS ke dalam aplikasi Anda dengan mudah.</p>

            <div class="endpoint">
                <h3>1. Create Payment</h3>
                <pre><code>GET /h2h/deposit/create?apikey=YOUR_API_KEY&reff_id=UNIQUE_ID&nominal=AMOUNT</code></pre>
                
                <h4>Parameters:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>apikey</strong> (required) - Your API Key</li>
                    <li><strong>reff_id</strong> (required) - Unique transaction ID (max 50 chars)</li>
                    <li><strong>nominal</strong> (required) - Amount in Rupiah (min 5000)</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h4>Response:</h4>
                <pre><code>{
  "status": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "txn_001",
    "reff_id": "your_ref",
    "nominal": 5000,
    "qr_string": "0002010102...",
    "qr_image": "https://...",
    "status": "pending",
    "created_at": "2024-01-01 12:00:00",
    "expired_at": "2024-01-01 13:00:00"
  },
  "code": 200
}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="endpoint">
                <h3>2. Check Payment Status</h3>
                <pre><code>GET /h2h/deposit/status?apikey=YOUR_API_KEY&reff_id=TRANSACTION_REF</code></pre>
                
                <h4>Response:</h4>
                <pre><code>{
  "status": true,
  "data": {
    "reff_id": "your_ref",
    "status": "pending/success/expired",
    "nominal": 5000,
    "qr_image": "https://...",
    "created_at": "2024-01-01 12:00:00",
    "expired_at": "2024-01-01 13:00:00"
  },
  "code": 200
}</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="endpoint">
                <h3>3. Lightweight Polling</h3>
                <pre><code>GET /h2h/deposit/poll?apikey=YOUR_API_KEY&reff_id=TRANSACTION_REF</code></pre>
                
                <h4>Response:</h4>
                <pre><code>{
  "status": "pending/success/expired",
  "message": "Status message"
}</code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <h3 class="card-title">Status Codes</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>pending</strong>: Waiting for payment</li>
                <li><strong>success</strong>: Payment completed</li>
                <li><strong>expired</strong>: QR Code expired</li>
                <li><strong>failed</strong>: Payment failed</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <h3 class="card-title">Contoh Integrasi (PHP)</h3>
            <pre><code>&lt;?php
$apiKey = "YOUR_API_KEY";
$reffId = "ORDER_" . time();
$nominal = 10000;

$url = "https://rpay.xyz/h2h/deposit/create?apikey=$apiKey&reff_id=$reffId&nominal=$nominal";

$response = file_get_contents($url);
$data = json_decode($response, true);

if ($data['status']) {
    $qrImage = $data['data']['qr_image'];
    echo "&lt;img src='$qrImage'&gt;";
} else {
    echo "Error: " . $data['message'];
}
?&gt;</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
